gomodel:SYNGO_4918  a    owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment     "Rationale: Figure 6A-C: KCNQ5 immunogold labeling in the primate dorsolateral prefrontal cortex showed localization at dendritic spines and dendrites. The omission of the primary antibody or substitution with non-immune serum abolished all reactivity.\n\nBased on the known transmembrane topology of this protein, \"integral component of ... membrane\" term was selected.. Experimental description: Brain tissue from four adult Rhesus macaques (10-22 y.o., female)\nKCNQ5 antibodies: Abcam Cat # ab66740; RRID:AB_1139413; Cat# ab57634; RRID:AB_944919 (not specified which one was used for the immuno-EM experiments)" , "Automated change 2024-03-14: GO:0099055 replaced by GO:0045211" ;
        lego:modelstate  "production" ;
        dc:contributor   "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2514-0216" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2286-1587" ;
